metatag_title: Blue Label Throne & Foot Spa Pedicure Chair for Nail Salon
metatag_description: Have your guests relaxing in style with the Blue Label Throne & Foot Spa from Michele Pelafas, Inc. - premium nail salon furniture, selected for style & comfort.
photo_alttext: Blue Label Throne & Foot Spa Pedicure Chair for Nail Salon
productdescription: Unprecedented,  Blue Label Pedicure Spa Redefines Luxury. Blue Label is the first and only Pedicure Spa that transcends equipment and enters into the realm of fine furniture and hospitality with the most sophisticated pedicure seating and integrated foot bath on the market today.   Its advanced features and special design are unrivaled, blending comfort, style, clean-ability, functionality and sanitation all in one gorgeous piece of furniture for the ultimate pedicure experience.  As you consider the possibilities for your new pedicure environment, imagine an alternative to what has been done before and to what is found in every other nail salon.  The pedicure world is truly ready for something new.  Something unique.  Something special.  Meet Blue Label.DISCOVER STYLEBlue Label gives the traditional pedicure throne new meaning with its timeless design, graceful posture and regal qualities.  The stunning shape and chic sensual curves distinguishes Blue Label from any other Pedicure Spa and is reminiscent of fine furniture found in hospitality.  Your guests will finally have a new reality for feeling pampered and posh.   Blue Label beckons, invites and cocoons with its extended high wingback, fully upholstered shell, smooth satiny foot bath, decorative nail heads and stained wooden legs.   Continue to imagine the possibilities:  hundreds of fabric choices, lush textures and intricate patterns.  Yes, Blue Label is both an experience and a design statement.  If you are looking to make a lasting impression, begin with Blue Label. DISCOVER TECHNOLOGYBlue Label's stunning design on the outside is matched with state-of-the-art technology on the in.  It's core boasts pipe-less jets for an invigorating yet sanitary foot bath with removable jet covers that simply twist off for easy cleaning.  Blue Label comes complete with a Cascading Auto-Fill spout to prevent over-flow and save water.  It offers a built-in shiatsu massage, adjustable seat and reclining back so guests can fade away behind the extended high back wings.  The senses are stimulated with built-in colored LED lights and Blue Tooth sound, allowing your guests to connect or disconnect, their choice.  An adjustable footrest for your technicians reduces stress and fatigue.  And finally, easy to use digital keypads give both the technician and the guest complete comfort and control for a personalized experience. DISCOVER QUALITYHand-crafted in the USA, Blue Label brings value that is indescribable yet indispensable.   Its sturdy frame and ergonomic seat cushions are composed of the most highly resilient polyurethane foam, luxurious commercial-grade fabric and Dacron book wrap.  Each piece has a special softness and support to give your guests the feeling that "comfort truly is king".   The integrated solid surface foot bath is smooth, non-porous, low maintenance and backed by a commercial 5-year warranty.  Our high-performance fixtures, fittings and jets come standard with Blue Label offering unsurpassed quality and superiority.  Blue Label bears the hallmarks of fine design, attention to detail and made with tender loving care.  Blue Label brings extraordinary design, innovation and quality to the global spa market.  International design appeal is yours today, discover the possibilities.  Discover Blue Label.

Affinity Spa Towels are fluffy soft, thick, and absorbent, yet they dry very quickly. These towels are woven to a plush 600 grams per square meter giving them the ultra soft feeling wash after wash.  Bath Sheet 35x70 Bath Towel 28x54 Hand Towel 17x30 Face Towel 12x12Make sure you wash your towels before you use them. For the first wash add 1/2 cup to 1 cup of white vinegar during the rinse cycle. Making sure you are pouring the vinegar into the water and not directly on the towels. We recommend using a mild laundry detergent as well as washing your white towels in warm water. Use about half the amount of detergent you normally would to prevent build up. Dry on cool setting, heat will cause your fibers to break down and become scratchy and rough.Do NOT use Softener. Softeners prevent the towel fibers from being able to absorb moisture, if you notice your towel smell or they seem to not be as soft as they once were, wash with 1 cup of vinegar to balance the PH levels back to normal.

productdescription:
Trendz styling bar is the space saving solution for a 4-person work station to fit in a tight space. This ingenious design integrates a check in and out area at the front of the bar with interchange-able decorative front panel. Each right and left styling bars are generously sized to fit 2 guests each side with optional free-standing table top mirrors. Each station includes 2 drawers, one for clips, combs and brushes, and one is heat insulated for a blow dryer and styling tools. Behind the bar is ample storage. Bar includes foot rest bar, toe kick lighting at the front greeting station and integrated electrical chase for easy hard-wiring on site. Electrical box cut-outs included. Electrical wiring by licensed electrician on-site by others.

Laminate Finish

Includes 4 table top mirrors size: 28" tall x 22" wide

Overall size: 9' wde x 11' front to back
Styling bar height: 34" high
Reception Desk Height: 30"

productdescription:
Fashionable. Distinct. Simply over the top. The plush and posh Carrie Swivel Pedicure Chair & Foot Spa combines fine furniture, modern comfort and technology giving and entirely new meaning to the word "pamper". The sweeping soft curves, tall back and tufted detail make this chair extra-ordinary for any salon or spa environment. Guests will receive a luxurious and relaxing hydrotherapy foot bath while nestled within the generously sized seating with its sculpted wing-back that offers guest privacy and sound absorption. The classic shape will enhance the architectural quality of any room and is available in different color palettes and fabric patterns. Carrie makes a gorgeous and dramatic design statement bringing with it, quality, style and innovation. Designed by Michele Pelafas, Inc. and lovingly made in the USA.

Standard Features:
-Grade A Fabric
-Upholstered Base with Stock White Solid Surface Top, Furniture Legs
-Chroma Jet Under-mount, Pearl White Acrylic Pedicure Sink with 2 Pipe-less Jets
-Adjustable Height Footrest Pad
-Faucet with Pull-out Spray Hose, Polished Chrome
-Foot Actuated Drain Kit, Polished Chrome
-Lumbar Pillow to Match Back Cushion Fabric

Also available without jets as foot soak only, deduct $496


Sink Features:
-Magnetic Pipe-less jets that are easy to remove, clean, sanitize and maintain water temperature so that no heater is needed
-Silent operation for enhanced relaxation
-Optional iFill system, the most advanced spa control system in the industry with an optional digital control, LED color changing light and water level sensor
-True Green Technology, energy saving

Plumbing Upgrades:
-Spa iFill w/Water Level Sensor, LED Light & Digital Control, $569
-Saniflo Premium Discharge Pump $418
-Cable Driven Drain Kit w/Control Handle to Release drain, $253

Designed by Michele Pelafas, Inc. and made in U.S.A

Size: 34"w x 65"d x 70"h

productdescription:
Pure clean and extra quiet, the Cloud Nine Pedicure Bench with its gorgeous back cushion detail is comfortable,ergonomic and includes our pipe-less reflexology foot bath to stimulate keypoints on the feet to release tension, restore balance and improve energy flowand wellness. The high style design with its soft over-sized pillow-topped back is matched with revolutionary hydrotherapy technologyto give you the assurance of clean water with every treatment. Pamper your guestswith a soothing and relaxing experience in the Cloud Nine Pedicure Bench!Optional LED color-changing light for effect. Custom colors and fabricsavailable. Choose a round pedicure sink with curved front face or a rectangularpedicure sink with a straight front face.

Handcrafted in the USA, our pedicure bench seating is composed of the most highlyresistant polyeurthane foam, commercial grade fabric and Dacron book wrap forunsurpassed quality and comfort. Each piece bears the hallmark of fine design,attention to detail and made with tender loving care for value that isindispensable.

NOTE:This sink is also available as a soaking tub (no jets), Deduct $560 from price

-DischargePump, Add $325

productname: Chroma Jet Pedicure Sink & Foot Spa
productdescription:
Chroma Jet™ Pedicure Sink is the essential pedicure sink for custom spa, beauty and hospitalityenvironments. This beautiful colored acrylic drop-in basin fits into any décor for custom applications and unique design projectswith its revolutionary Magna-Jet Technology. Chroma Jet™ combinesa hydrotherapy foot bath for a soothing and relaxing experience with theassurance of pure, clean water and a gorgeous spa aesthetic. Available ina rainbow of colors. Adjustable height footrest in whiteincluded.

  • Modern rectangular drop-in sink
  • Fits into any decor with its gorgeous color options, clean lines and elegant shape
  • Generous sizing and flat bottom is comfortable for the feet
  • Smooth touchable acrylic surface is non-porous and easy to clean
  • Fiberglass reinforced backing for strength

Features:

  • Unique silent operation for enhanced relaxation
  • Magnetic Pipe-less jets are easy to clean and sanitize
  • Spa-iFill™ System option with Remote Digital control, LED Color changing light and water level sensor is the most advanced spa control system in the industry today
  • Designed for commercial applications with hydrotherapy foot bath requirements
  • Maintains water temperature, no heater is needed
  • Includes adjustable height footrest
  • True Green Technology, energy saving
  • High reliability - Use with confidence and worry free!
  • Designed by Michele Pelafas, Inc and made in U.S.A
Also available with a free-standing pedicure sink vanity (shown with sink) in it's coordinating solid surface color, add $1296 for the vanity.

Sink size: 24" wide x 22" front to back, 10" high
Vanity Size: 30" wide x 25" front to back, 16" high

productdescription:
The Aiden customize-able bar collection has a clean modern look that is features a 1" thick white solid surface top that contrasts with the horizontal linear grain of the laminate for an approachable, simplistic statement piece that functions to meet the most stringent nail environments. The bar is priced and shown as a 3-person bar with 3 technician storage cabinets in the back, however the bar length can be made up to 252" long for 6 persons with technician storage cabinets sold separately so that you can truly customize the bar to your specific requirements.

Standard features for this model shown and priced:
-3 person bar, 126" w x 18" d x 34" h
-Includes 3 technician storage components that each have 3 drawers
-Laminate finish and 1" white solid surface top

Customize the bar to fit your needs:
2 person bar: 84" w x 18" d x 34" h, Starting at $2156
3 person bar: 126" w x 18" d x 34" h, Starting at $3234
4 person bar: 168" w x 18" d x 34" h, Starting at $4312
5 person bar: 210" w x 18" d x 34" h, Starting at $5390
6 person bar: 252" w x 18" d x 34" h, Starting at $6468

Technician storage cabinets, choose one:
Single drawer with storage below, $655 each
Double drawer with storage below, $807 each
Triple drawer unit, $858 each

Optional upgrades:
Foot rail, $78 per linear foot
Electrical chase, $45 per linear foot

Optional add-ons:
UV Gel lamp cut-outs, $288 set of 2 per person
Pencil drawer, $166 per technician
Upholstered Armrest, $106 per person

Can also be made 40" high for a taller bar height or 30" high for a standard height. Call for pricing.

Audrey pedicure chair and foot spa combines fine furniture with technology for the ultimate pedicure experience. Audrey truly is the definition of elegance with all of the class and sophistication of its namesake yet with all of the functional requirements of a pedicure spa. Guests will receive a luxurious and relaxing hydrotherapy foot bath while nestled within the fully upholstered enclosed sides and top that offer guest privacy and sound absorption. The classic shape will enhance the architectural quality of any room and is available in different color pallets and fabric patterns. Audrey makes a gorgeous and dramatic design statement bringing with it, quality, style and innovation.

Standard Features:
-Upholstered Base on Furniture Legs with White Solid Surface Top
-Grade A Fabric
-Diamond Jet Drop-in/Vessel Round White Acrylic Sink with 2 Pipe-less Jets
-Adjustable Height Footrest Pad
-Faucet with Spray Hose, Polished Chrome
-Foot Actuated Drain Kit, Polished Chrome
-Lumbar Pillow

NOTE: This sink is also available as a soaking tub (no jets), Deduct $496 from price

Sink Features:
-Magnetic Pipe-less jets that are easy to remove, clean, sanitize and maintain water temperature so that no heater is needed
-Silent operation for enhanced relaxation
-Optional iFill system, the most advanced spa control system in the industry with an optional digital control, LED color changing light and water level sensor
-True Green Technology, energy saving

Built-in Upgrades
-Back Massage with Remote Control, $448

Plumbing Upgrades:
-Spa iFill w/Water Level Sensor, LED Light & Digital Control, $569
-Saniflo Premium Discharge Pump $418
-Cable Driven Drain Kit w/Control Handle to Release drain, $253

Designed by Michele Pelafas, Inc. and made in U.S.A

Audrey built-in pedicure chair and foot spa combines fine furniture with technology for the ultimate pedicure experience. Audrey truly is the definition of elegance with all of the class and sophistication of its namesake yet with all of the functional requirements of a pedicure spa. Guests will receive a luxurious and relaxing hydrotherapy foot bath while nestled within the fully upholstered enclosed sides and top that offer guest privacy and sound absorption. The classic shape will enhance the architectural quality of any room and is available in different color pallets and fabric patterns. Audrey makes a gorgeous and dramatic design statement bringing with it, quality, style and innovation.

-Laminate Base (Platform Step sold separately)
-Grade A Fabric
-Diamond Jet Drop-in/Vessel Round White Acrylic Sink with 2 Pipeless Jets

Microdermabrasion uses a fine jet of crystals to gently and painlessly peel the skin to reveal new softer skin with improved texture.  Self-enclosed system with vacuum suction removes crystals along with dead skin cells. Microdermabrasion also promotes the production of new skin cells in the basal (deepest) layer of the dermis, cleans pores and stimulates collagen networking that can further rejuvenate skin's appearance. This non-invasive procedure is simple, quick, suitable for all skin types, and has virtually no discomfort or down time for recovery.  Microdermabrasion can be used successfully on light or dark skin and is beneficial for hyperpigmentation, acne/acne scars, fine lines, wrinkles, oily skin, enlarged pores, stretch marks, and surgical scars.  Can be placed on tabletop, stainless steel cart, or atop the OxyMax oxygen concentrator machine.  For use by licensed professionals only. productdescription:
Prima Pedicure Sink Vanity with integrated Purjet Pedicure Sink is a permanently plumbed free-standing fixture that can be used with your own custom built-in 7" high platform and your own supplied chair. It features a fully upholstered curved base, solid surface top and is plumbed through the wall (with a gravity drain and discharge pump) or the floor in front of your platform, offering you the essential pedicure sink basin for your spa, beauty and hospitality environment. With its revolutionary Magna-jet Technology and Pipe-less jets, you will have the assurance of pure, clean water while providing your guest with a soothing and relaxing experience in this gorgeous and generously sized hydrotherapy foot bath. Sink includes 2 pipe-less magna-jets, easy plumbing access with removable shell, faucet, foot-actuated drain and an adjustable height footrest. Discharge pump sold separately. Prima Pedicure Sink Vanity is also available without jets for a natural foot soak sink. Platforms and chairs sold separately. For gravity drains, a discharge pump may be required, please consult your plumber. Chair seat heights of 18" are recommended. Select your vinyl upholstery color, solid surface color and sink color to complete your look. Bonus! Easily change your look with a replacement upholstered shell without having to re-plumb! Our replacement shells can give you an instant update seasonally or when you are ready for a change! Replacement shells sold separately.

-Includes adjustable height foot rest
-True Green Technology, energy saving
-High reliability - use with confidence and worry free!

productdescription:
Pure clean and extra quiet, the Social Butterfly Pedicure Bench with its gorgeous back cushion detail is comfortable, ergonomic and includes our pipe-less reflexology foot bath to stimulate key points on the feet to release tension, restore balance and improve energy flow and wellness. The high style design with its soft upholstered curved back frame and inland accent fabric is matched with revolutionary hydrotherapy technology to give you the assurance of clean water with every treatment. Pamper your guests with a soothing and relaxing experience in the Social Butterfly Pedicure Bench! Optional LED color-changing light for effect. Custom colors and fabrics available. Choose a round pedicure sink with curved front face or a rectangular pedicure sink with a straight front face.

Hand crafted in the USA, our pedicure bench seating is composed of the most highly resistant polyeurthane foam, commercial grade fabric and Dacron book wrap for unsurpassed quality and comfort. Each piece bears the hallmark of fine design, attention to detail and made with tender loving care for value that is indispensable.

Standard Features:
-Grade A Fabric for Seat & Back
-Laminate Base including Seat Base, Sink Base & Step
-Purjet Rectangular Acrylic Pedicure Sink with 2 Pipe-less Jets
-Push-pull drain kit, Polished Chrome
-Adjustable Height Footrest
-Single Lever Swivel Faucet, Polished Chrome
-Lumbar Pillow
-Remove-able Front Sink Face for Plumbing Access
-Remove-able Seat and Back Cushions for Plumbing Access
NOTE: This sink is also available as a soaking tub (no jets), Deduct $560 from price

Optional Plumbing & Sink Upgrades:
-Round Diamond Jet Sink with Curved Remove-able Front Panel, Add $198
-Faucet with Pull-out Spray Hose, Add $157
-Discharge Pump, Add $325
-Cable Driven Drain Kit, Add $212
-LED Color Changing Light, Spa-Fill System with Water Level Sensor & Digital Control, Add $475

Optional Built-in Upgrades:
-Back Massage with Remote, Add $350
-Built-in Storage Drawer, Cubbie or Opening for Hot Towel Cabinet above Step, Call for Pricing
-Laminate or Upholstered Divider or Side Arms with optional drink holder built-into the arm, Call for Pricing
-Integrated Table for Drinks & Cell Phones, Add $135
-Convenience outlet in toe kick to plug in appliances & curing lamps, Add $198
-Additional Accent Pillows, Call for Pricing
-Removable Arm rest with Drink Holder, $220
-Fabric Upgrades & COM, Call for Pricing
-Solid Surface Top on Sink Base or Step, Call for Pricing
-Solid Surface for Entire Base, Call for Pricing
-Mosaic Tile Base, Call for Pricing

Listed Price is for a (1) Single-person bench. Available in any amount of groupings from a (1) Single-person Bench to any amount of persons.

Single unit size: 44"w x 53"d x 57"h. Custom sizes available

productkeywords: Tifany Double Pedicure Bench
productdescription:
Pure clean and extra quiet, the Tiffany Double Pedicure Bench, for two persons, with its gorgeous back cushion detail is comfortable, ergonomic and includes our pipe-less reflexology foot bath to stimulate key points on the feet to release tension, restore balance and improve energy flow and wellness. The high style design with its statement-making back frame and inlaid accent fabric is matched with revolutionary hydrotherapy technology to give you the assurance of clean water with every treatment. Pamper your guests with a soothing and relaxing experience in the Double Tiffanys Pedicure Bench for two! Optional LED color-changing light for effect. Custom colors and fabrics available.

Hand crafted in the USA, our pedicure bench seating is composed of the most highly resistant polyeurthane foam, commercial grade fabric and Dacron book wrap for unsurpassed quality and comfort. Each piece bears the hallmark of fine design, attention to detail and made with tender loving care for value that is indispensable.

Standard Features:
-Grade A Fabric for Seat & Back
-Laminate Base including Seat Base, Sink Base & Step
-Purjet Rectangular Acrylic Pedicure Sink with 2 Pipe-less Jets
-Push-pull drain kit, Polished Chrome
-Adjustable Height Footrest
-Single Lever Swivel Faucet, Polished Chrome
-Lumbar Pillow
-Remove-able Front Sink Face for Plumbing Access
-Remove-able Seat and Back Cushions for Plumbing Access
NOTE: This sink is also available as a soaking tub (no jets), Deduct $560 from price

Optional Plumbing & Sink Upgrades:
-Round Diamond Jet Sink with Curved Remove-able Front Panel, Add $198
-Faucet with Pull-out Spray Hose, Add $157
-Discharge Pump, Add $325
-Cable Driven Drain Kit, Add $212
-LED Color Changing Light, Spa-Fill System with Water Level Sensor & Digital Control, Add $475

Optional Built-in Upgrades:
-Back Massage with Remote for two person, Add $798
-Built-in Storage Drawer, Cubbie or Opening for Hot Towel Cabinet above Step, Call for Pricing
-Convenience outlet in toe kick to plug in appliances & curing lamps, Add $198
-Additional Accent Pillows, Call for Pricing
-Fabric Upgrades & COM, Call for Pricing
-Solid Surface Top on Sink Base or Step, Call for Pricing
-Solid Surface for Entire Base, Call for Pricing
-Mosaic Tile Base, Call for Pricing

Listed Price is for a (2) Two-person bench.

Overall size: 84"w x 53"d x 57"h. Custom sizes available

productdescription:
Pure clean and extra quiet, the Well Dressed Pedicure Bench with its gorgeous back cushion detail is comfortable,ergonomic and includes our pipe-less reflexology foot bath to stimulate keypoints on the feet to release tension, restore balance and improve energy flowand wellness. The high style design with its button-tufted and linear stitching on the back is matched with revolutionary hydrotherapy technologyto give you the assurance of clean water with every treatment. Pamper your guestswith a soothing and relaxing experience in the Well Dressed Pedicure Bench!Optional LED color-changing light for effect. Custom colors and fabricsavailable. Choose a round pedicure sink with curved front face or a rectangularpedicure sink with a straight front face.

Handcrafted in the USA, our pedicure bench seating is composed of the most highlyresistant polyeurthane foam, commercial grade fabric and Dacron book wrap forunsurpassed quality and comfort. Each piece bears the hallmark of fine design,attention to detail and made with tender loving care for value that isindispensable.

-Grade AFabric for Seat & Back

-LumbarPillow
-Remove-ableFront Sink Face for Plumbing Access

NOTE:This sink is also available as a soaking tub (no jets), Deduct $560 from price

Optional Plumbing & Sink Upgrades:
-RoundDiamond Jet Sink with Curved Remove-able Front Panel, Add $198

OptionalBuilt-in Upgrades:
